title: The Voice Behind the Music
leadParagraph: Surabhi Dashputra is a versatile Indian singer and content creator whose soulful voice has captivated over 60,000 monthly listeners on Spotify.
bodyParagraphs: With a career spanning multiple genres, Surabhi has lent her powerful vocals to iconic Bollywood film soundtracks and released original music that deeply resonates with audiences. Her hit tracks "Dhul Gaye" and "Mangoge Na?" have collectively crossed 2.6 million streams.
